# Build-only D1 seed data (generated by tools/gen-puzzles.mjs, loaded manually
# into D1). Kept out of the repo so it isn't publicly served from the site root
# and doesn't spoil upcoming daily boards. Regenerate + reload with:
#   node tools/gen-puzzles.mjs <enable1.txt> data/puzzles.sql <START YYYY-MM-DD> [DAYS]
#   npx wrangler d1 execute njdt-leaderboard --remote --file=./data/puzzles.sql
